[SHORT DESC]
Heals variably depending on the weather.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Heals 1/2 max HP in no weather, 2/3 in sun, and 1/4 in hail, rain, and sandstorm.
</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/recover">Recover</a> is an equivalent move unaffected by weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/slack_off">Slack Off</a> is an equivalent move unaffected by weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/softboiled">Softboiled</a> is an equivalent move unaffected by weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/milk_drink">Milk Drink</a> is an equivalent move unaffected by weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/heal_order">Heal Order</a> is an equivalent move unaffected by weather.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/roost">Roost</a> is an equivalent move, but removes all Ground-type immunities.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/moonlight">Moonlight</a> is identical.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/synthesis">Synthesis</a> is a Grass-type equivalent.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/wish">Wish</a> is an equivalent move, but HP is recovered at the end of the second turn.</p>